00:37:49.930 --> 00:37:52.839
In fact it was big scientists of the world
united to-to for the freedom of Soviet democratic

00:37:52.839 --> 00:37:53.839
dissidents.

00:37:53.839 --> 00:38:03.369
And I have to say that it was not easy to
struggle not only because of KGB, but because

00:38:03.369 --> 00:38:09.730
many people in the free world believed that
Soviet Union is forever; it will never change;

00:38:09.730 --> 00:38:12.640
and we have to know how to live in peace with
the Soviet Union.

00:38:12.640 --> 00:38:17.370
And that's why they were saying, "Trade is
better than, when we have trade there is no-no

00:38:17.370 --> 00:38:21.440
wars. So let us have trade with them."

00:38:21.440 --> 00:38:28.470
Here Senator Jackson comes with the amendment
to connect all the trade agreements of United

00:38:28.470 --> 00:38:31.720
States of America with the creation of freedom
in Soviet Union.

00:38:31.720 --> 00:38:38.140
And even businessmen and President, then it
was Nixon, speak against it. They speak that

00:38:38.140 --> 00:38:44.241
we don't want these restrictions. We cannot
dictate to Soviet Union what-what is freedom;

00:38:44.241 --> 00:38:49.210
they have their own principles but we want
to live in peace with them.

00:38:49.210 --> 00:38:54.450
And we, and Andrei Sokolov was very good with
them and he had to explain again and again

00:38:54.450 --> 00:38:58.230
to the free world that the only way that there
will be stability and peace is if it will

00:38:58.230 --> 00:38:59.369
support Soviet dissidents.

00:38:59.369 --> 00:39:06.760
As long as it is a totalitarian regime, it
will need you as the enemy. So they will have

00:39:06.760 --> 00:39:10.849
trade with you, but they will build everything
so their own people will hate you because

00:39:10.849 --> 00:39:15.190
otherwise this regime cannot survive. And
that was a big battle.

00:39:15.190 --> 00:39:19.880
And that's why I say that what Google is doing
now is so important.

00:39:19.880 --> 00:39:26.320
Some days ago I published an article in support
of Nobel Prize Committee which gave the Nobel

00:39:26.320 --> 00:39:28.910
Prize to Chinese dissident in prison.

00:39:28.910 --> 00:39:36.430
And again if you know immediately after this
there was again voices the West, what it has

00:39:36.430 --> 00:39:39.079
to do with peace? Why-why tell it to Chinese
people what to do?

00:39:39.079 --> 00:39:44.540
And I -- that article I went back to the logic
was dissidents of the Soviet Union explaining

00:39:44.540 --> 00:39:51.329
why for the security of United State of America,
it is very important what is happening with

00:39:51.329 --> 00:39:53.680
human rights there in-in China.

00:39:53.680 --> 00:39:58.810
So I want to say that that is in fact one
battle; one battle which continues; there

00:39:58.810 --> 00:40:06.329
is no borders in this battle. There must be
people for whom physical survival is not the

00:40:06.329 --> 00:40:14.650
most important thing; who have principles,
identity for which they are ready to-to-to

00:40:14.650 --> 00:40:17.940
sacrifice everything, and who believe in freedom.

00:40:17.940 --> 00:40:22.450
And these people have to be supported by all
the free world and that is the only way to

00:40:22.450 --> 00:40:26.670
guarantee freedom and stability in the world.

00:40:26.670 --> 00:40:31.910
Well I say it in about, in about 10 minutes
all my three books are about it so those of

00:40:31.910 --> 00:40:37.810
us who want to dissent why it is better, please
go to Google find my three-three books.

00:40:37.810 --> 00:40:46.030
One is about my experience in Soviet prison,
another is about the case for democracy, and

00:40:46.030 --> 00:40:48.030
the third is about defending identity.

00:40:48.030 --> 00:40:56.690
So it's all these topics together today, then
I was in Israeli governments when Prime Minister

00:40:56.690 --> 00:41:02.089
Netanyahu proposed me again to go to politics,
I said, "No-no I was nine years in prison.

00:41:02.089 --> 00:41:05.540
I was nine years in these early politics.
