I told him, "Look, I was in four different

00:41:10.840 --> 00:41:12.760
Israel governments and that why I resigned."

00:41:12.760 --> 00:41:17.380
In comparison, I was in four different prisons
and never resigned. They asked me many times

00:41:17.380 --> 00:41:20.089
to sign letter to resign and I refused to
resign.

00:41:20.089 --> 00:41:21.089
So probably something wrong.

00:41:21.089 --> 00:41:25.350
And then he said, "So what you want?" I said,
"I want to be chairman of The Jewish Agency."

00:41:25.350 --> 00:41:27.771
That's why I'm the chairman of Jewish Agency.

00:41:27.771 --> 00:41:33.630
Jewish Agency is unique organization which
tries, which is global table of Jewish people

00:41:33.630 --> 00:41:39.370
and the Israeli government which tries to
connect between Israel and Jewish communities

00:41:39.370 --> 00:41:40.680
all over the world.

00:41:40.680 --> 00:41:45.560
And I know the power of this connection; I
know how this connection inspired us and gave

00:41:45.560 --> 00:41:51.750
us strength to fight for freedom and I know
that it is also true today.

00:41:51.750 --> 00:41:56.240
So thank you for inviting me. I'm glad to
be here and see that in two days from now

00:41:56.240 --> 00:42:02.010
there will be a Garry Kasparov speaking. My
great friend the last, in the last, when I

00:42:02.010 --> 00:42:07.700
