00:42:07.700 --> 00:42:08.700
[laughter]

00:42:08.700 --> 00:42:12.170
'cause so the life has very interesting twists.

00:42:12.170 --> 00:42:17.339
I am very glad that you are a place which
attracts leading democratic dissidents. They

00:42:17.339 --> 00:42:23.010
need your support. You have a very powerful
weapon in your hands which gives opportunity

00:42:23.010 --> 00:42:27.380
to make dissemination information much easier,
unbelievably easier.

00:42:27.380 --> 00:42:33.140
But what the biggest problem was, was how
to reach Soviet people in the Soviet Union

00:42:33.140 --> 00:42:39.069
with our truth, and today you have this weapon
which also can be used by our enemies.

00:42:39.069 --> 00:42:43.569
So don't let it [ ] our enemies and keep supporting
freedom of the world.

00:42:43.569 --> 00:42:44.569
Thank you.

